HEADWORD: Usbeks
<hw>Us"beks</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
}</mhw> <pos>n. pl.</pos> <fld>(Ethnol.)</fld> <def>A Turkish tribe
which about the close of the 15th century conquered, and settled in,
that part of Asia now called Turkestan.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>Uzbecks</asp>, and <asp>Uzbeks</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
